Gold Fields Expects Recovery in Beatrix Mine Output

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-05-19T13:47:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/gold-fields-expects-recovery-in-beatrix-mine-output-correct-.html
(Corrects to say recovery expected at company’s Beatrix
mine, not Driefontein.)  Gold Fields Ltd. (GFI)  expects to see a
recovery in production of the precious metal from its Beatrix
mine in  South Africa  this quarter, Chief Executive Officer Nick Holland said.  Output from Beatrix was lower than planned during the
company’s fiscal first quarter, he said in a speech in
Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carli Lourens in Johannesburg at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  